{"tid":381091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係咪呢世搭MTR都無得坐?","createTime":"2017-08-30T15:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T18:29:19.000Z","uid":42894,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"459e435b3bc57b7c69ec54d1d44834d930130bdd","tid":381091,"uid":42894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"我平日返學搭MTR一向可以唔坐就唔坐<br />\n因為我知我呢啲年紀坐成日比人睥<br />\n咁我今日係中環上車個時 架車岩岩到站等開<br />\n大把位 我又覺得攰 而且等等完佐就直接返工<br />\n所以先揀個普通位坐下 難得坐下玩下手機<br />\n點知仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩開車就比個c奶叫我讓坐比個老人家<br />\n個老人家就話唔洗唔好意思 不過我起身之後佢就直接去坐<br />\n然後我見到對面關愛座有2個三十幾歲牛高馬大既男人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但點解叫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個好恰啲定女人易講啲？<br />\n<br />\n我係咪呢世都唔洗指意係MTR坐？"},{"pid":"4775ba9df0cc1d8aa50fce201b84b3b41eab86e2","tid":381091,"uid":45374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"直接講我轉頭返工會好攰。<br />\n<br />\n你條廢老睇死你都係返屋企撚雀，唔好阻住後生既推動社會發展<br />\n<br />\nBtw 渣ge"},{"pid":"176b123ddb6a6c85e549f319de40e5cf197a43c2","tid":381091,"uid":16883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"你做廢老個時就有得坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896d82bfc7e615895c59ce60cf40fef826cf544a","tid":381091,"uid":10408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:01:20.000Z","msg":"想坐咪坐，到站起身走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e70c5cc0e9c1fea519209c65b8e97aa3c3af6f8","tid":381091,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbcb32a808ce80aa150224c70f8d72fc37c86bea","tid":381091,"uid":113921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"有冇咁多c奶？<br />\nc奶會咁沙卜？"},{"pid":"97213fe20a57ed2bbc07c6be9331bff68e7cc184","tid":381091,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"唔洗理c9<br />\n<br />\n成日都扮好人搵人賣單"},{"pid":"56e5d8f93e36d51ef8126424457f332553ba3aeb","tid":381091,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗理c9<br />\n<br />\n成日都扮好人搵人賣單</blockquote><br />\n埋"},{"pid":"34ba17e543585756cd784eed539836b7fa0d5e97","tid":381091,"uid":22402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:18:16.000Z","msg":"依家坐地鐵點都會帶個earphone <br />\n唔撚會理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐就坐"},{"pid":"a9545b1abd8a34fb3f631c0480ceee4726025396","tid":381091,"uid":36701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家坐地鐵點都會帶個earphone <br />\n唔撚會理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐就坐</blockquote><br />\n有次我瞓咗都畀人拍返醒呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11b30d1d4a4c352f885b5351a937e68c84633d0","tid":381091,"uid":141985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家坐地鐵點都會帶個earphone <br />\n唔撚會理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐就坐</blockquote><br />\n有次我瞓咗都畀人拍返醒呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望佢2眼再瞓過"},{"pid":"3fe4e39f52e10c503062e04cc3c09801fd8ead7c","tid":381091,"uid":36701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家坐地鐵點都會帶個earphone <br />\n唔撚會理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐就坐</blockquote><br />\n有次我瞓咗都畀人拍返醒呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望佢2眼再瞓過</blockquote><br />\n瞓到懵撚咗好自然企咗起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條廢老仲要唔該都冇聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64314210453cd276cc236538a4a656503901bca","tid":381091,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家坐地鐵點都會帶個earphone <br />\n唔撚會理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐就坐</blockquote><br />\n一樣 六七十歲個樣西過西炒飯果啲死廢老一定唔會讓<br />\n但真係好老個樣又慈慈祥祥果啲就會讓"},{"pid":"4e1677628066b40578864de15163963a16d925e8","tid":381091,"uid":129039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家坐地鐵點都會帶個earphone <br />\n唔撚會理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐就坐</blockquote><br />\n有次我瞓咗都畀人拍返醒呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望佢2眼再瞓過</blockquote><br />\n瞓到懵撚咗好自然企咗起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條廢老仲要唔該都冇聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我都試過<br />\n喺輕鐵瞓瞓下有個師奶叫我讓比個呀伯<br />\n當時未醒晒 傻下傻下就企起身<br />\n之後諗諗下先發覺唔對路 仲要佢兩個本身都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩個呀伯都幾有禮貌 係咁講唔該同叫我坐番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e1b1825d12bbb82f76392360334d58c074c299","tid":381091,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:30:06.000Z","msg":"我試過m痛坐關愛座比個大陸呀嬸用<span style=\"color: red;\">普通話</span>叫我起身<br />\n話我坐緊關愛座 應該要讓比個抱住bb嘅女人坐<br />\n但人地明明同老公一齊企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抱得攰咪比個老公抱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更何況個女人都耍手擰頭話唔洗<br />\n我打死唔讓 用廣東話話我m痛 佢就繼續喺到口up up 話依家啲後生真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉個頭到太子 我同嗰對夫婦落左車 個呀嬸自己坐撚左個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781f1993ef05bc76654aec6af428c1ba3ce273c4","tid":381091,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"叫得讓坐個啲都係低下階層人士"},{"pid":"cc2725a7d5e72d3a35665051fc8d8d1d0d053782","tid":381091,"uid":140762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T19:09:15.000Z","msg":"學下大陸設有女士車廂  香港應該設有廢老車廂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767bd4132fc164d4cb267bec0a5ff3a7841ddb87","tid":381091,"uid":42894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家坐地鐵點都會帶個earphone <br />\n唔撚會理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐就坐</blockquote><br />\n有次我瞓咗都畀人拍返醒呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49846f807389d8b43d3b15ab6d0ac693489e27f7","tid":381091,"uid":42894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇咁多c奶？<br />\nc奶會咁沙卜？</blockquote><br />\n我都係第一次咁喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}